"Two Million Minutes" produced a few years

00:04:57.000 --> 00:05:01.380
ago, the amount of time that you're gonna
spend in high school, actually not in the

00:05:01.380 --> 00:05:06.840
school, but over four years and the quality
of learning is drastically changing.

00:05:06.840 --> 00:05:13.669
